[Genotyping will be decisive in confirming the suggested connection between the 2 events. Tracing back the route and chronology of ASF introduction into Germany's eastern state of Mecklenburg-Vorpommern is required for lessons to be learned and targeted control measures undertaken, hopefully preventing further spread. To this end, comparing the respective locations of both cases, and 2 points in time, will be helpful. The latter refers to the estimated time of ASF virus introduction into the affected farm, and the estimated time of the wild boar's death (see Mod.CRD's commentary in 20211118.8699737). - Mod.AS

